Offense
sword- declares an atack action to an enemy piece ur max range is determined by a dice throw, doesnt ignore walls
axe- declare an atack action once on any enemy piece if you do a dice throw higher or equal to 4
bow- declare an atack action on any enemy piece u throw a dice to hit on that specific range can hit throught walls
dagger- if ur in the same tile as an enemy piece instantly kill once



utility
boots- throw an extra dice for movement
goat- leaves a goat on the current tile if an enemy piece passes through they must declare a atack action on the goat if they lose they lose that piece
robe- ignore any piece or action declared besides movement
cape- make one power up on the map disappear

defense
shield- fully deny one single atack action during enemy turn once
chestplate- plus 2 to ur defensive dice throws in case an enemy declares an atack action
helm- immunity to bow



definitions
atack action- garenteed kill low range